HEADWORD: Equites
<hw>Eq"ui*tes</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>n. pl</pos> <ety>[L., pl. of
<ets>eques</ets> a horseman.]</ety> <fld>(Rom. Antiq.)</fld> <def>An
order of knights holding a middle place between the senate and the
commonalty; members of the Roman equestrian order.</def>⟦br⟧
